182
00:10:18,850 --> 00:10:20,140
Absolutely.

183
00:10:20,290 --> 00:10:21,760
Trust me.

184
00:10:23,220 --> 00:10:24,930
But, I think...

185
00:10:25,030 --> 00:10:26,250
