- No.

206
00:11:39,210 --> 00:11:39,910
Enough!

207
00:11:39,930 --> 00:11:41,850
OK, enough. I give up.

208
00:11:42,140 --> 00:11:43,510
Enough.

209
00:11:43,530 --> 00:11:44,980
Good that you surrender.

210
00:11:46,410 --> 00:11:48,180
