248
00:14:06,940 --> 00:14:09,490
I'm not, I'm just asking frankly.

249
00:14:09,510 --> 00:14:11,160
You love him, don't you?

250
00:14:11,710 --> 00:14:14,900
It's not to that level, I just like him.

251
00:14:16,210 --> 00:14:17,390
You love him.

252
00:14:17,420 --> 00:14:19,880
