302
00:16:35,000 --> 00:16:38,420
Soon, those two will sit with us.

303
00:16:38,980 --> 00:16:40,610
I want to show you...

304
00:16:40,630 --> 00:16:43,370
I'm nobler than he is,
that shameless.

305
00:16:43,960 --> 00:16:45,330
Soon.

306
00:16:45,550 --> 00:16:46,470
Pew.

307
00:16:46,500 --> 00:16:48,690
I think we shouldn't bother them.

308
00:16:49,140 --> 00:16:50,470
Just mind our own business.

309
00:16:50,490 --> 00:16:51,710
No way.

310
00:16:51,800 --> 00:16:53,230
He took away my boyfriend.

311
00:16:53,270 --> 00:16:54,650
I won't admit defeat.

312
00:16:56,500 --> 00:17:00,850
Soon those two will sit with us.

313
00:17:04,130 --> 00:17:06,410
Sawasdee krub,
have you guys have a table yet?

314
00:17:06,470 --> 00:17:08,810
Not yet. Can you get one for me?

315
00:17:09,740 --> 00:17:14,040
Here, just nice.
Have a sit first and I'll take your order.

316
00:17:14,060 --> 00:17:14,860
OK.

317
00:17:14,890 --> 00:17:16,430
Thank you.

318
00:17:16,450 --> 00:17:18,490
Come, don't be afraid of him.

319
00:17:36,960 --> 00:17:38,600
Thank you.

320
00:17:55,100 --> 00:17:56,730
What are you laughing at?

321
00:17:58,640 --> 00:18:00,440
