323
00:18:03,180 --> 00:18:06,180
We'll find out if
they're interested or not.

324
00:18:06,590 --> 00:18:07,790
How?

325
00:18:07,990 --> 00:18:09,410
This.

326
00:18:21,700 --> 00:18:22,650
