327
00:18:22,670 --> 00:18:25,150
Are you using money to lure them?

328
00:18:25,790 --> 00:18:28,660
I'm willing to do anything to win.

329
00:18:29,330 --> 00:18:31,230
But isn't that too much...

330
00:18:31,540 --> 00:18:32,940
by using money?

331
00:18:32,970 --> 00:18:34,350
No it's not.

332
00:18:34,450 --> 00:18:36,450
Compare to him
snatching away my boyfriend.

333
00:18:39,090 --> 00:18:42,090
Sawasdee krub,
P'. Can we sit with you?

334
00:18:42,340 --> 00:18:44,460
Don't you want to sit at that table?

335
00:18:45,260 --> 00:18:49,320
Well, that table has nothing
interesting than this table.

336
00:18:50,990 --> 00:18:53,610
Sure thing, sit next to me.

337
00:18:58,170 --> 00:18:59,620
I'm Thum.

338
00:18:59,990 --> 00:19:01,110
I'm Max.

339
00:19:01,300 --> 00:19:05,390
My name is Pew,
