340
00:19:06,930 --> 00:19:08,660
So what's your name?

341
00:19:09,490 --> 00:19:11,160
He's beautiful too.

342
00:19:12,450 --> 00:19:13,870
I'm Kawee.

343
00:19:15,020 --> 00:19:16,890
That's a nice name.

344
00:19:19,380 --> 00:19:21,570
I don't have the strength to drink.

345
00:19:21,600 --> 00:19:23,630
What should I do?

346
00:19:26,880 --> 00:19:28,700
Let me help you with that.

347
00:19:29,370 --> 00:19:30,300
OK.

348
00:19:30,720 --> 00:19:33,400
