353
00:19:48,210 --> 00:19:49,670
I can feed you.

354
00:19:49,700 --> 00:19:52,100
No need, just sit there.

355
00:19:52,770 --> 00:19:54,230
Don't pay attention to him.

356
00:19:55,050 --> 00:19:56,990
Let us cheers together.

357
00:19:59,260 --> 00:20:01,100
I want to know you better.

358
00:20:05,830 --> 00:20:08,200
That's enough, my mouth is full.

359
00:20:09,150 --> 00:20:10,500
Thank you.

360
00:20:10,850 --> 00:20:12,870
You're taking me for a drink?

361
00:20:14,250 --> 00:20:16,100
I couldn't sleep.

362
00:20:16,350 --> 00:20:17,580
Come now.

363
00:20:17,600 --> 00:20:19,070
Drink with me for awhile.

364
00:20:20,880 --> 00:20:22,540
OK, OK.

365
00:20:22,760 --> 00:20:23,810
Just for a little while.

366
00:20:23,840 --> 00:20:25,330
I need to open
the cafe tomorrow morning.

367
00:20:25,640 --> 00:20:29,850
I know, Mr. Phupha,
the handsome barista.

368
00:20:30,710 --> 00:20:31,890
Come.

369
00:20:34,340 --> 00:20:36,010
Mai, Ai'Mai.

370
00:20:36,030 --> 00:20:37,000
Yeah?

371
00:20:37,960 --> 00:20:39,470
That's N'Kawee.

372
00:20:41,230 --> 00:20:42,890
The N'Kawee that you like.

373
00:20:44,040 --> 00:20:45,500
There's a guy hitting on him.

374
00:20:46,520 --> 00:20:48,760
Don't worry, buddy.
I'll deal with this.

375
00:20:49,140 --> 00:20:50,770
You can mess with lots of people.

376
00:20:51,210 --> 00:20:52,930
And you have to mess
with the one my friend likes.

377
00:20:55,080 --> 00:20:56,470
