378
00:21:09,420 --> 00:21:11,670
N'Kawee, Sawasdee krub.

379
00:21:12,450 --> 00:21:13,760
P'Phupha?

380
00:21:14,870 --> 00:21:16,680
What a coincidence again.

381
00:21:17,300 --> 00:21:20,310
It's just so happened that
we don't have any table.

382
00:21:20,840 --> 00:21:22,280
Can we sit together?

383
00:21:23,900 --> 00:21:25,010
Sure thing.

384
00:21:25,030 --> 00:21:26,400
Please sit.

385
00:21:27,780 --> 00:21:29,640
Find a chair to sit.

386
00:21:30,600 --> 00:21:32,170
Is there anyone sits here?

387
00:21:32,200 --> 00:21:33,130
I'll take it, OK?

388
00:21:42,740 --> 00:21:44,720
Are you here with your friends?

389
00:21:44,740 --> 00:21:46,210
I never met them before.

390
00:21:47,330 --> 00:21:48,640
Not a friend.

391
00:21:49,230 --> 00:21:51,910
I want to be more than
just a friend with Khun Kawee.

392
00:21:55,660 --> 00:21:57,040
In that case...

393
00:21:57,890 --> 00:21:59,820
You have to get disappointed.

394
00:22:00,680 --> 00:22:01,910
Why?

395
00:22:02,210 --> 00:22:04,870
