396
00:22:05,490 --> 00:22:06,950
Still single...

397
00:22:07,480 --> 00:22:09,130
but in a moment...

398
00:22:09,860 --> 00:22:12,070
he'll have a boyfriend, right?

399
00:22:15,410 --> 00:22:17,020
Yes.

400
00:22:17,920 --> 00:22:20,900
Are you hitting on Kawee too?

401
00:22:23,820 --> 00:22:25,990
I'm sure to call it a hit on...

402
00:22:26,470 --> 00:22:28,150
but it might be close.

403
00:22:32,190 --> 00:22:34,080
For that reason,
looking at you today...

404
00:22:35,270 --> 00:22:37,990
