470
00:26:03,430 --> 00:26:04,840
Maybe.

471
00:26:07,200 --> 00:26:08,790
But you said it quite loud.

472
00:26:10,890 --> 00:26:13,180
Are you saying that they only
gonna send you home, is that is?

473
00:26:15,560 --> 00:26:19,100
But I think P'Phupha likes you for sure.

474
00:26:19,510 --> 00:26:21,820
You must tell P'Paew about this.

475
00:26:21,850 --> 00:26:23,170
What are you talking about?

476
00:26:23,730 --> 00:26:25,740
I'm saying according
to what I've seen.

477
00:26:26,200 --> 00:26:28,660
He was so jealous
in the bar just now.

478
00:26:28,680 --> 00:26:30,240
He even wants to send you home.

479
00:26:30,550 --> 00:26:33,210
He starts to have
heart for you for sure.

480
00:26:33,280 --> 00:26:35,450
He starts to like you for sure.

481
00:26:35,640 --> 00:26:38,120
You need to get closer to him.

482
00:26:38,140 --> 00:26:41,080
I guarantee that he'll fall for you.

483
00:26:42,320 --> 00:26:44,170
You're such a beauty.

484
00:26:49,510 --> 00:26:51,090
What now?!

485
00:26:51,530 --> 00:26:53,530
I forgot that I'm heartbroken.

486
00:26:53,560 --> 00:26:55,040
My tears are out when I talk.

487
00:26:55,110 --> 00:26:56,420
I'm sad.

488
00:26:56,440 --> 00:26:57,960
I'm heartbroken.

489
00:26:57,990 --> 00:27:00,160
You two brothers
are really the same.

490
00:27:00,250 --> 00:27:00,870
Let's go home!

491
00:27:00,900 --> 00:27:02,940
I don't want to.
I want to drink some more.

492
00:27:03,070 --> 00:27:04,420
Let's go home!

493
00:27:06,100 --> 00:27:06,920
OK.

494
00:27:16,200 --> 00:27:17,660
Ai'Tai.

495
00:27:18,210 --> 00:27:19,530
Wake up.

496
00:27:20,690 --> 00:27:22,690
Wake up...

497
00:27:22,740 --> 00:27:25,180
Don't disturb me, I want to sleep.

498
00:27:25,200 --> 00:27:27,260
You can't sleep here. Get up.

499
00:27:27,610 --> 00:27:30,830
Don't disturb me,
I'm sleeping here.

500
00:27:35,250 --> 00:27:37,190
- Get up.
- What's your problem?

501
00:27:37,220 --> 00:27:39,140
Stand still.

502
00:27:39,310 --> 00:27:41,560
What's your problem?

503
00:27:42,200 --> 00:27:44,390
What are you doing?

504
00:27:44,420 --> 00:27:45,270
What's your problem?

505
00:27:46,790 --> 00:27:48,270
Ai'Tai!

506
00:27:54,840 --> 00:27:57,190
What's on my leg?

507
00:28:00,660 --> 00:28:03,250
Ai'Tai, don't look!

508
00:28:03,280 --> 00:28:05,370
Close your eyes.

509
00:28:10,490 --> 00:28:12,250
What's your problem?

510
00:28:24,490 --> 00:28:25,880
What are you smiling at?

511
00:28:27,480 --> 00:28:28,860
Well...

512
