528
00:29:19,270 --> 00:29:20,560
You...

529
00:29:24,340 --> 00:29:26,180
No need to be shy.

530
00:29:27,740 --> 00:29:29,580
If...

531
00:29:29,800 --> 00:29:32,370
you want to see mine as
a recompense, you can.

