539
00:29:54,760 --> 00:29:56,920
Shut up, just sleep.

540
00:30:04,260 --> 00:30:06,560
If you wanna see mine as
recompense, just let me know.

541
00:30:06,700 --> 00:30:08,570
Shut up!

542
00:30:15,180 --> 00:30:16,600
My heart was shaking again.

543
00:30:16,630 --> 00:30:18,240
